flowRoot.flowPara: If you need to punish someone then do it bijective. Best thing is not to attack a person physically or in the mainframe, or with cyberwar... you could risk his or your life. There are seldom cases, for example if they want to (cyber-) [ rape | attack ] your girl..., in this case it is possibly ok to defend yourself and younger against the offender. Keep in mind that you defend yourself without causing permenent harm. Maybe the offender is remote controlled. See cards t1,... t*

If there is something like death sentence for example in texas then and would kill an innocent you would find that out to late, then the whole state could sentenced to death to. In Switzerland there are no official death sentences.
